<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Imaduddin Learning Hub</title>
<style>
body{
margin:0;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#334155);
color:white;
padding:40px;
}
.container{
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
}
h1{font-size:48px;}
p{color:#cbd5e1;}
.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:30px;
}
.card{
background:#1e293b;
padding:20px;
border-radius:18px;
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
}
input{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin-top:10px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
}
button{
margin-top:12px;
padding:12px;
width:100%;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<h1>Imaduddin Learning Hub</h1>
<p>Learn Basic to Advanced English with IELTS Preparation</p>

<div class="grid">
<div class="card"><h2>📘 Basic English</h2><p>Grammar, speaking, easy sentences.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h2>📗 Intermediate</h2><p>Tenses, writing, conversations.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h2>📙 Advanced</h2><p>Fluent speaking, vocabulary.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h2>🎯 IELTS Zone</h2><p>Reading, Writing, Listening.</p></div>
</div>

<div class="grid">
<div class="card">
<h2>🔐 Student Login</h2>
<input placeholder="Email Address">
<input placeholder="Password" type="password">
<button>Login</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>📜 Certificates</h2>
<p>Earn certificates after course completion.</p>
<h2>🤖 AI Speaking Checker</h2>
<p>Improve speaking daily.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
